{"tid":758660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Rubio: 中國啲新聞都黐線既 好似恐怖電影咁 佢哋對自己人都咁 你可以期望佢哋點對待其他國家既人？","createTime":"2018-07-28T02:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T06:44:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"de229810156e8f3ddcb53b32242da3e8b1225c5d","tid":758660,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TXTgxtFr6Eo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTXTgxtFr6Eo&d=6BTf8xs85qiJDV7eXNNnQ7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ec11b529\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TXTgxtFr6Eo</a><br />\n<br />\nIn reaction to testimony by UN Ambassador Kelley E. Currie at the commission, he said that news from Beijing was akin to a &ldquo;horrible movie.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;[T]hese are crazy things, things we&rsquo;ve read about that used to happen thousands of years ago, or things that happened under regimes in a science-fiction novel,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;These are some of the most horrifying things that are happening in the world today. That it doesn&rsquo;t lead newscasts in the country and around the world in and of itself is problematic.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This is outrageous. And it&rsquo;s hypocritical. And the international organisations that stand by and say nothing &ndash; why? Because China went into somebody&rsquo;s country and built a road or a bridge or maybe bribed them and gave them a billion dollars to be quiet and go along. This is just &ndash; this is sick.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n最後：&quot;this is how you treat your own people, how do you expect them to treat people in some other part of the world？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2018/07/28/china-silencing-overseas-critics-amid-crackdown-muslim-region-says-us-journalist-family-detained/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2Fchina-silencing-overseas-critics-amid-crac